### Get hello text
GET http://localhost:8080/hello

### Get error
GET http://localhost:8080/error

### Get some path that does not exist
GET http://localhost:8080/unknownpath

### GET users
GET http://localhost:8080/user

### GET user 111
GET http://localhost:8080/user/111

### GET user 999
